  <header class="article-header">
    <h1>There's One Sleep Trick That Actually Works — Here's the Science Behind Why</h1>
    <div class="by-line">
      <a title="Max Plenke's Profile" class="link-author avatar avatar-small" href="http://mic.com/profiles/188702/max-plenke">
        <img alt="Max Plenke's avatar image" class="no-share-btns" src="http://media3.mic.com/MmRkOGM1M2ZlYSMvR0tfRWRseWtnWmtrdVpPWUtVdno1V1k4WnFBPS8yNXgyNS9zbWFydC9odHRwczovL3MzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20vcG9saWN5bWljLWltYWdlcy8xOTFhZmFhMDY2NDBhODY4YTNlN2YzMWZiZTU3NjZhNzEwNmExNWRmMTFiYWQwOGMyZDc1MDI0ZTA1OTA5ZWU5LmpwZw==.jpg">
      </a>
      By
      <a title="Max Plenke's Profile" class="link-author name" href="http://mic.com/profiles/188702/max-plenke">Max Plenke</a>
      <time datetime="2015-11-06T19:17:42.000Z" pubdate="">November 06, 2015</time>
    </div>
    <div class="share-facebook-twitter subhead">
      <span class="fb-like-container-text">Like Mic on Facebook:</span>
      <span class="fb-button">
        <div class="fb-like-top fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/thefutureisnowbymic" data-width="300" data-keen-tracking-name="subhed" data-keen-social-channel="facebook_future" data-show-faces="false" data-send="false" data-layout="button"></div>
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div id="article-body" class="article-body share-media-toolbar-block"><div class="share-media share-media-side-fold">
